title: DAZ3D Genesis 3 Superhero Pack
description:
23944 - DG Iray Action Fabrics Shader 
http://www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/23944

Today's Man of Metal or Amazing Woman leads a busy life. Between fighting crime and turning up for the latest photo op, they don't always have time to jet off to the local Super Hero Supply Store when they need a quick costume change. What's a super hero on a deadline to do? DG Iray Action Fabrics to the rescue with 95 shader presets in the latest damage resistant fabrics like durable leather, high gloss vinyl, flexible neoprene, high impact metal, and breathable mesh. There are 33 patterns in metallic, non metallic, or mesh. Each preset has a color chosen, but don't stop there. Create a coordinating Marvelous League and make your own varieties by picking any color you need in the Base Color. Also included are 10 tiling presets and 1 base shader reset for your utility belt. Your Super Heroes will always be fresh and ready for a hectic, action packed day. All of the included shader presets use the Iray UberSurface shader that comes with Daz Studio 4.8+.

What better way to blow off the cobwebs of Winter, amble in the Spring, sprint through the Summer or sedately wind your way through Autumn than on your bicycle? And who can go cycling without their proper attire? Dark-Elf & Undead Studios are proud to present Bike Race Outfit for Super Bodysuit for Genesis 3 Male(s), a set of lycra cycle wear and cycling shoes for all your cycling needs. With 5 different color and pattern schemes, as well as specially made cycling shoes with 7 texture variations, the possibilities are endless.

Guardian for the Super Bodysuit comes with an extremely detailed set of textures, complete with details for realistic stitching and tailoring. Enhanced HD morphs add even more natural wrinkles to the suit, and new cowl morphs will add more variation to your heroic style. New material zone options allow for new and greater versatility to your Super bodysuit for more completely original looks. 


32919 - Cetus X Textures for Super Bodysuit for Genesis 3 Females 
http://www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/32919

A set of Iray textures for the Super Bodysuit for Genesis 3 Females and the skirt from the Superhero Add-On set with a futuristic feel. The set includes 2 default designs for the Bodysuit and Skirt in 4 colour options. Change up the default design with the included additional 8 material style option presets which let you quickly and easily change the suit appearance. Matching Boot mats are also included!
